# Adding New shadcn/ui Components

To add new components from [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/), use the `pnpx shadcn@latest add <component-name>` command. This will add the component's source code to `src/components/ui` and install any necessary dependencies.

## Example

To add a `button` component, run the following command in your terminal:

```bash
pnpx shadcn@latest add button
```

This will create `[src/components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/button.tsx)`.
